Task 1: Username Formatter

Input a username and:

Convert it to uppercase.
Convert it to lowercase.
Convert it to title case.
Task 2: Email Validator

Input an email address and:

Check if it starts with a letter.
Check if it ends with .com.

(Hint: Use startswith() and endswith())

Task 3: Character Counter

Input a sentence and:

Count how many times the letter 'a' appears.
Count how many times the letter 'e' appears.

(Hint: Use count())

Task 4: Search a Character

Input a word and:

Find the position of a given character.
Display "Character Not Found" if it doesn't exist.

(Hint: Use find())

Task 5: Password Checker

Input a password and check:

Is it only alphabets?
Is it only digits?
Is it alphanumeric?

(Hint: Use isalpha(), isdigit(), isalnum())

Task 6: Name Decoration

Input your name and:

Display it centered within 20 characters using *.
Display it left-justified within 20 characters using -.
Display it right-justified within 20 characters using -.
Task 7: Text Converter

Input a sentence and:

Convert it to uppercase.
Convert it to lowercase.
Swap uppercase to lowercase and vice versa.
Task 8: Replace Words

Input a sentence and:

Replace all occurrences of "Python" with "Java".

(Hint: Use replace())

Task 9: Roll Number Formatter

Input a roll number and:

Pad it with zeros to make it 10 digits long.

(Hint: Use zfill())

Task 10: Case Analyzer

Input a word and check:

Is it all uppercase?
Is it all lowercase?
Is it title case?

(Hint: Use isupper(), islower(), istitle())
